### DIGEMID Medicine Search API - Ejemplos HTTP
### Usar con extensiones como REST Client para VS Code

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/medicines


### Health Check - Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### Health Check - General
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### Health Check - Medicines Service
GET {{apiUrl}}/health


### Buscar medicamento - APRONAX en Lima
POST {{apiUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_medicamento": "APRONAX",
  "departamento": "LIMA",
  "provincia": "LIMA",
  "distrito": "PUENTE PIEDRA",
  "limite_resultados": 10
}


